## Coding Rules

1. After your task is complete, upsert the sessionProgress.md progress tracker following the strict rules set in the progressTrackerRules.md

2. Take a TDD approach when possible/practical by writing tests before implementation. This will help you think through the intended use.

3. Before considering a task complete, run all tests to verify the state of our codebase.

4. ASK ME FOR HELP OFTEN! It's ok, i'd love to help!

5. When you fail to fix and issue 3x in a row, take a step back and reassess your path. Don't be afraid to ask me for assistance or guidance! This is a team effort! Pair coding is fun and efficient!
